CLIENTS WINDOWS
1ST WINDOWS:
- The title for each clients windows was
"ENTER YOU NAME"
[Name input box]  [Accep button]

- If all clients type their name and click "accept" button, then in the the host servers display box there should be a display text that says:
(Client name) is ready
(Client name) is ready
(Client name) is ready


2ND WINDOWS:
- If a client click the accept button, the client windows will change to this:

- Title of each clients windows is
 "Client: (name of the client)"

[Bid button] [Sell button]  [Time Left: (the time of the auction from the host)]

                 Item for BIDDING:
(Display box for all list of items that will be selled from all clients.)


             Item you are SELLING:
(Display box for all the items that you are selling.)


                 Highest BIDDER:
(Display box for who is the highest bidder for each item in the auction list.)

Reminders:
- The Auction will not start if the "Host server didn't click the start button".
- The "Bid and Sell" button will not be clickable if the host server doesn't start the auctions or click the start button.


3RD WINDOWS:
- If the host server click "Start" button, the input time will start and the "Bid and Sell" button from the Clients Windows will be clickable/accessible.

- If any clients click the "Sell" button, then the clients windows will add a new windows name "SELLING" that look like this:

-Title of the windows "SELLING"

Item: [Input box]  Price: [Input box]     [Accept button]

- If the clients (seller) click the "accept" button, the new windows "Selling" will be closed and the host server will be notified and display a text of:
Examples;(John Wick is the seller)

Selling: House Php 500 [John Wick]
Selling: Shoes Php 250 [John Wick]

- but for all clients except for the "Seller", the text will be display to the "Item for BIDDING".
Examples;
                  Item for BIDDING:
House, 500[John Wick]
Shoes, 250[John Wick]

- but for the Seller(John Wick), the text will be display into "Item you are SELLING"  display box.
Examples;
House Php500
Shoes Php250



- If the clients(Thor) click the items(House) listed in the "Item for BIDDING"  and click the "Bid" button, there will be a new windows "BIDDING".
- In the new windows "BIDDING", is look likes this:

Title of the windows "Bidding"

House:[Input box]  [Accept button]









